	     <tr><td id=headerrow colspan=2 class=mform valign=top><a name=/db/item.html?item=2157&mid=102092270681621>&nbsp;</a><a id=sj href=/db/item.html?item=2157&mid=102092270681621>RE: The cape</a> <a id=fs8 href=/db/item.html?item=2157&mid=102092270681621#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a>
	     <br clear=all><small>Posted @ Thu, May 9th 1:46 AM 2002</small></td></tr>
	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=84649><span id=Scholar>Troodon</span></a><br><b><span id=Scholar>Scholar</span></b><br><span id=notbold>709 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [3.20]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>Um, about the toolboxes... they have no weight reduction, and weigh 3.5 stones... while tailored backbacks weigh only 3 stones and have 10% weight reduction.&nbsp;&nbsp;The only thing the deluxe toolboxes are especially good for (and this is what I use them for) is increasesing the item capacity of your bank vault.  For carrying they're fairly worthless, as the cost too much weight (especially if you're a caster with low carrying capacity or a monk who doesn't want a weight penalty).  Unless you need a cheap container that has a giant capacity...<br><br>However, the real reason the value of HQ bear pelts dropped has to do with Luclin.  HQ hopperhides can be used in place of HQ bear pelts now in the tailored backpack recipe.  HQ hopperhides drop off of any saurek hopper in Shadeweaver's Thicket, at a much higher rate than HQ bear pelts drop off bears.  Simple economics; a common supply that can be used as a substitute for a rarer ingredient will reduce the demand, thus the price, of the rarer ingredient.<br><br>Goes without saying this will also cause the selling price of tailored backpacks to drop.</p>&nbsp;<br><span class=sm>----------------------------</span><br>Troodon, AKA Zararazu Twoflower, Level 66 Iksar Monk, Solusek Ro<br><br>My profile: <a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=91426" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=91426</a></td></tr>
